# hacker hive

    sets of agents sharing purpose.
    that's a hive.

## what is the hacker hive?

the hacker hive is an initiative to make housing cooperatives (like [BSC](http://bsc.coop)) modeled after [hackerspaces](http://hackerspaces.org/wiki/List_of_Hacker_Spaces). [i](https://www.dinosaur.io), as a student at UC Berkeley, invite all hackers of Berkeley (see [Hack@Berkeley](http://hackersatberkeley.com/), [CSUA](http://www.csua.berkeley.edu/), [OCF](https://secure.ocf.berkeley.edu/), [IEEE](http://ieee.berkeley.edu/), and probably you) to join us in making a cooperative living system near the [northside of UC Berkeley](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Northside,_Berkeley,_California).

